@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kgsmar(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp(0.14))
    tmp = 0.58
    v2 = (0.68 * wp.cos(v2))
    v2 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.00 + tmp + 0.17) * v0))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = wp.cos((v1 / v0))
    v1 = 0.65
    data[tid] = v0
